This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses reinforcement learning techniques to improve the translation quality. The paper may also be relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural machine translation models and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with sentiment classification of Twitter data.
